{"tid":651882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"勁過英雄聯盟，南北韓在今屆世乓錦標賽八強賽中碰頭，即場合體，同躋4強","createTime":"2018-05-03T12:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T02:31:47.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e24d833399b26c4671e2e7493570c9a6b68049b","tid":651882,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"世界乒乓球錦標賽8強　兩韓突組聯隊齊闖準決賽<br />\n<br />\n南北韓在《板門店宣言》中承諾，推動在各領域的合作交流。正在瑞典舉行的世界乒乓球錦標賽，原定女子團體賽8強由南韓對北韓爭逐4強席位，但賽前兩隊決定以「韓國」聯隊身份參賽，直接躋身4強。這是時隔27年後，南北韓再次在世界乒乓球錦標賽組隊出戰。<br />\n<br />\n大韓乒乓球協會週四（3日）宣佈兩韓聯隊參賽的決定，4強對手將是烏克蘭與日本的勝方。聯隊由5名南韓選手及4名北韓選手組成，若順利奪得獎牌，所有選手都會獲獎，並在頒獎儀式上同時升起南北韓的國旗。據悉，南北韓兩隊早一日已與國際乒聯商討改為聯隊的決定，早上更在總部駐紮的酒店進行一場混合組隊友誼賽，象徵性打成3比3平手。到了正式比賽時，兩隊只舉行簡單的握手儀式，就沒有進行任何正式賽事。<br />\n<br />\n今次並非南北韓乒乓球隊首度攜手聯隊，早於1991年在日本千葉舉行的世界錦標賽，兩韓便曾聯隊參戰，當時由南韓玄靜和、北韓李粉姬兩大名將擔綱的南北聯軍，更加擊敗中國勇奪女團金牌。不過，今次在比賽中途突然聯隊，而大會竟然又批准，此情況極之罕有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180503/photo/bknint-20180503182010171-0503_17011_001_01b.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180503%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180503182010171-0503_17011_001_01b.jpg%20&h=cc5c4c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6FjjpHs8aik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6FjjpHs8aik&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm50%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e46ae229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6FjjpHs8aik</a>"},{"pid":"ed88163dca3a83b5ddb0689f1445f8b155497b77","tid":651882,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"北韓可唔可以幫手踢世界杯？"},{"pid":"3fa240bce7205c03b42f7fca700c28b8ee28db0d","tid":651882,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed88163dca3a83b5ddb0689f1445f8b155497b77","tid":651882,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"北韓可唔可以幫手踢世界杯？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"應該可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79cd9aa2000c7e7da2e1cfa12c0abd6f8e7b8aa","tid":651882,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"世界盃隊隊都大唔撚踼，溝埋一齊打和進級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc2bab266f28d67f3a95d6cc1958719b4e7c859","tid":651882,"uid":15993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c79cd9aa2000c7e7da2e1cfa12c0abd6f8e7b8aa","tid":651882,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"世界盃隊隊都大唔撚踼，溝埋一齊打和進級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙同阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n兩個同時攞世盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b5a6e71b5300b48822d936a651a043dd64638","tid":651882,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc2bab266f28d67f3a95d6cc1958719b4e7c859","tid":651882,"uid":15993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c79cd9aa2000c7e7da2e1cfa12c0abd6f8e7b8aa","tid":651882,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"世界盃隊隊都大唔撚踼，溝埋一齊打和進級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙同阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n兩個同時攞世盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"最後係地球隊攞世界盃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bbc160591945763fc7311a4f74ac9125895f5c","tid":651882,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"